5
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,079
Rebe.

6
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:40,680
-What?
-Were you really dealing at school?

7
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,400
Were you, Valerio?

8
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:52,359
You two... come in.

9
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:59,040
-Azucena, good morning.
-Good morning, Begoña.

10
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,640
I'd like to talk to you.
Do you have a few minutes?

11
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:04,480
Actually,
I have an important matter to see to.

12
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,480
Not more important
than what I have to say.

13
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,520
I'll be right with you--

14
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:11,280
I can always go over your head
and speak to the board.

15
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:14,159
