41
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:38,159
Yeah, you showed me photos.
It's as big as Central Park.

42
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:41,520
You can't ask someone
you barely know to put people up--

43
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:44,919
What do you mean?
We were engaged for a night.

44
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,360
Although, you two are pretty close,
right?

45
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,639
We just hooked up a few times.

46
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:59,560
-I mean--
-Yeah, we just hooked up. Got it.

47
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,840
I would only stay temporarily.

48
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,639
OK, sure. Why not?

49
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,079
Nobody would know
if someone hadn't snitched.

50
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:32,399
Valerio and Rebeka were selling drugs,
and Polo reported it.

51
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:35,040
You're blaming him
for doing what's right?

52
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,600
Samuel, Guzmán.

53
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,600
Come with me, please.

54
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,279
Us?

55
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,240
Now.

56
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,480
Look, Azucena.

57
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:52,000
You can make an argument for expelling us,
but these two?

58
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,920
-We didn't do anything!
-I warned you.

59
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,680
I said there'd be zero tolerance. 

60
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:58,600
And yet, you've been tormenting him
since Christmas.

61
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:01,279
This is bullshit.
Polo's mother's behind it.

62
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:04,279
She was in here right before us.
Am I right?

63
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:09,240
