Forget about him already.

186
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,799
He's already ruined your year,
your life, and everything.

187
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,679
-How can I forget?
-Distance.

188
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:44,159
Focus on what matters now,
like your family coming home.

189
