-Be like Guzmán. Move on.
-Bullshit.

190
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,679
Here.

191
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:56,000
-What're you doing?
-Close your eyes. Close them!

192
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,919
All done.

193
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:07,159
-What's all done?
-Polo doesn't exist.

194
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:09,360
Polo who? I don't know any Polo.

195
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,320
-Hey, neither do I.
-See?

196
00:14:11,399 --> 00:14:12,639
It really works, huh?

197
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,399
Can I have a napkin?

198
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:27,039
You really have some balls
showing up here.

199
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:29,080
I just want to dry off, Omar.

200
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,480
And I want you to go.

201
00:14:31,519 --> 00:14:32,759
For your own good.

202
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,720
Leave!

203
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:46,559
-Mom!
-Baby, tell me you have a cig.

204
00:14:46,639 --> 00:14:49,679
I'm jonesing for one so bad,
I almost smoked parsley.

205
00:14:53,679 --> 00:14:57,159
