but you didn't pick up.

210
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:15,080
-Shit, that was you?
-Of course it was me.

211
00:15:20,399 --> 00:15:21,600
You smell so nice.

212
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:24,480
And you're so beautiful.

213
00:15:29,559 --> 00:15:30,399
What?

214
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:32,519
Nothing.

215
00:15:33,679 --> 00:15:35,440
Come on. I know that look.

216
00:15:39,399 --> 00:15:41,279
I got kicked out of school.

217
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:44,200
What do you mean? When?

218
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,840
Now. Well, earlier.

219
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,240
Why?

220
00:15:50,279 --> 00:15:51,360
