221
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,399
Fucking shit.

222
00:15:58,279 --> 00:16:01,159
Well, know what? Fuck school.

223
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:04,879
If you know what you're doing,
you don't need school.

224
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:07,919
You've been doing an awesome job
running the family business.

225
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,240
At your own level, on a small scale,
but awesome.

226
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:16,200
From now on,
it's mother and daughter, hand in hand.

227
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,840
Hi.

228
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,039
Holy shit, Mom.

229
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:32,000
Get mad at her later.

230
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,480
Let's go outside.

231
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,799
Sorry. I didn't know what else to do.

232
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,639
What's so hard to understand?

233
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:44,519
We do understand.

234
00:16:45,799 --> 00:16:48,120
Look at you. You got expelled. So what?

235
00:16:48,639 --> 00:16:49,679
Big fucking deal!

236
00:16:50,039 --> 00:16:53,080
You'll graduate next year.
I don't have next year.

237
00:16:53,159 --> 00:16:54,480
What don't you get?

238
00:16:54,559 --> 00:16:58,000
Fine, you don't have next year.
What do you want to do?

239
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:02,639
Your mom says you want time
by yourself. That's a shitty plan.

240
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:09,240
Guzmán... none of you
will ever understand.

241
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:13,119
You can do whatever the hell you want.

242
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:17,079
If you don't want to study, don't.
I don't even care if you want to skydive.

243
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,960
But don't isolate yourself, please.

244
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:22,160
Because, if you really are dying...

245
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:26,480
I can't believe
you'd want to spend your time alone.

246
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:29,799
Without your family, your friends,
and Omar.

247
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:37,160
Ander.

248
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:40,000
-Damn it, Ander.
-Leave me alone, please.

249
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:49,920
I can't take it anymore.

